Results.ReviewText: I bought this product two years ago and have not chosen any other brand or other nescafe coffee since. It is simply the best coffee on the market. Perfection. Nothing comes close to it. I love my Gold Blend.
Results.Title: My morning must have.

Results.ReviewText: I have been buying Nescafé Gold Blend for years why settle for anything less.  I have tried other brands from time to time and have always regretted it.  In my opinion you can’t buy a better instant Coffee.
Results.Title: Nescafé Gold Blend

Results.ReviewText: I have been drinking Nescafe gold blend for probably 30 years and the change has not been for the better. I do not like this half as much as the original gold blend. I have never bought any other brand ever
Results.Title: Bring back the original gold blend

Results.ReviewText: Always our favourite, Nescafe Coffee is like a beacon to me along the aisles of the supermarket , their coffee brands never disappoint, tried others but always come back to Nescafe ad it cannot be bettered.
Results.Title: Assured Quality

Results.ReviewText: I bought this recently, and I’m glad I did. I usually have 2 cups of coffee in the mornings, never more, so I make sure I use a really good coffee. And what better than this smooth, but flavoursome Nescafe!
Results.Title: Great taste!

Results.ReviewText: Swapped to Nescafe Gold Blend a couple of months ago and am so pleased with it have already bought more.  Also love your refill pouches as it offers a cheaper way to purchase your coffee and saves on waste.
Results.Title: Lovely strong taste

Results.ReviewText: I had to look closely at the new labelling to ensure I had picked the right coffee. Even so I find the fantastic taste I am used to with Nescafe Gold Blend and look forward to years of drinking this product
Results.Title: Fantastic Taste

Results.ReviewText: My favorite instant coffee is NESCAFÉ GOLD BLEND. A perfect mug with super powers I am ready to face the day. I stick with Nescafé and have done for years because nothing can beat it and it is inexpensive.
Results.Title: Perfect Instant Coffee for me

Results.ReviewText:
this coffee is perfect quality, it has a delicious taste,
Depending on your taste buds,if you enjoy strong coffee add 1 and half tsp fulls to 2 tsp full but if you enjoy weak cofee  just add 1 tsp coffee.
Results.Title: Nescafe gold blend

Results.ReviewText: I bought this for our builders to have a better quality coffee as they are all avid coffee drinkers rather than tea (unusual).  They seem to love it as they never turn down a cup however many I offer them!
Results.Title: Our builders love it !

Results.ReviewText: This coffee is great in the morning , when i wake up , go to work ,it's the first thing i get ready , the smooth rich flavour slips down warming me up and starts to wake me up ready to take the days work .
Results.Title: gold blend

Results.ReviewText: I ALSO BUY GOLD BLEND COFFEE ALWAYS STOCK UP IN MY CUPBOARDS I DIDNT NOTICE IT HAD CHANGE TILL I NOTICE THE JAR THE COFFEE IS THE SAME BUT LEAVES LIKE A BLACK MARK IN BOTTOM OF CUP WHICH IT NEVER DID BEFOR
Results.Title: Better

Results.ReviewText: I have been using Nescafe Gold for quite a few years now, it's got a great taste, smooth and tasty, I even converted my son who never drunk coffee in his life, now he only drinks gold, no more Tea for him
Results.Title: brilliant

Results.ReviewText: I am a coffee drinker and Nescafé gold blend is one of my favourite brands.  A lovely smooth taste I can make it as strong or mellow as I like it depending on my mood.  I always have a jar in my cupboard.
Results.Title: I love my coffee

Results.ReviewText: I had been looking for a nice tasting decaff coffe and this is the best I have found.  it has a smooth mellow taste, with no hint of chicory.  it is well balanced and satisfying.  I am so glad i found it.
Results.Title: Great taste

Results.ReviewText: We buy this in work in huge containers and I'd still choose to drink it at home. This is saying something as I'm quite fickle with food and drink and get bored very easily. It's the yard stick of coffee.
Results.Title: Great everyday coffee

Results.ReviewText: I usually buy Nescafe Gold blend and today I purchased the new jar and loved it.  It was a lovely cup of coffee, full of flavour.  I would definately purchase this again and also sample the other ranges.
Results.Title: Rich flavour

Results.ReviewText: Thought I would try two jars in case it was the first one that was dreadful. I have always drunk Gold Blend but no more, plus I cannot hold or get the lid off easily. Why change something so successful?
Results.Title: Absolutely awful.

Results.ReviewText: I have been using nescafe original for more than 10 years and the flavour and taste are amazing. I need only nescafe when i wake up and in the afternoon.  The beat coffee i have had so far and i love it
Results.Title: Morning boost

Results.ReviewText: I was visiting a friend and she made me a cup of this coffee, which was different to my usual brand. After tasting it I was converted! It tastes as delicious as it smells, perfect way to start your day!
Results.Title: Rich aroma!

Results.ReviewText: I have started stocking up when my local morrisons have ht in special and a great price at £5 for a 200g jar, A delicious coffee full bodied coffee that kick starts my day and keeps me refueled throught
Results.Title: Love the distinctive new jar

ClientResponses.Response: That's not what we like to hear but thank you for letting us know what you think of the changes.

Results.ReviewText: Before transformation Coffee taste lovely,i couldn’t stop drink it. It has velvety taste. Now it taste different,stronger(doesn’t mean better) as a longterm Customer it sadly doesn’t taste good anymore.
Results.Title: Taste different.

Results.ReviewText: This coffee is the favourite in my house.  I've tried many other brands when I see offers at the supermarket but we still go back to this brand.  Perfect coffee and wonderful taste.  Thank you Nescafe!!
Results.Title: Love this coffee!!

Results.ReviewText: I drink a mixture of french press and instant coffee. Whenever I'm feeling lazy I always reach for Gold Blend for my instant coffee. It's the perfect taste for me, full bodied and not bitter. I love it.
Results.Title: Favourite instant coffee!

Results.ReviewText: Bought gold blend or decades but recent changes to recipe will make me look elsewhere. Whoever at nescafe thought this was a good idea needs to be moved from product ‘improvement’
Results.Title: Changed a winning recipe

Results.ReviewText: This the instant coffee that always delivers. No matter whether it’s the first cup made from the jar, or the last, the taste is always rich and satisfying. That is why I always come back to gold blend.
Results.Title: Gold blend - gold standard

Results.ReviewText: We enjoy Nescafe Gold Blend so much that my wife and I never travel anywhere without it. We recently had the privilege to go on a cruise around the med so we drank Gold Blend in ten different countries
Results.Title: it is all we drink

Results.ReviewText: We have been regular drinkers of Nescafe Gold Blend for many years, and, although we have tried different coffees, we always come back to our favourite.  The aroma when you open a new jar is wonderful.
Results.Title: Our favourite

Results.ReviewText: I bought this new coffee jar over a month ago for the first time. The coffee is much better.More smooth and tasty coffee to drink especially in the mornings. I have just bought another jar yesterday !
Results.Title: Perfect and smooth coffee

Results.ReviewText: My son drinks a lot of coffee and is quite a connosierre,  he doesn't like strong coffee so neacafe gold is perfect it is smother and mild without losing the flavour, it's a family favourite for us .
Results.Title: Lovely and smooth
